# ðŸ“Š Data Jobs Market Analysis Dashboard (2024)

![Dashboard Page 1](images/Dashboard.png)

## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project analyzes **millions of job postings from 2024** related to the data industry, including roles such as:

- Data Engineer  
- Data Analyst  
- Data Scientist  
- Machine Learning Engineer  
- Business Analyst  

The objective of this dashboard is to transform large-scale raw job market data into actionable insights regarding demand, salary trends, work modality, and geographic distribution.

Built entirely in **Power BI**, this project demonstrates data transformation, modeling, and business insight generation.



